# Maldives Monetary Authority (MMA) Statistics Database API
# Docs / API key signup: https://database.mma.gov.mv/api/docs
# Used by the (planned) Maldives tourism statistics fetch script -- see
# the TODO in the top-level README.md.
#
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your real bearer token there.
# .env.local is gitignored (see .gitignore's "!.env.local.example"
# exception) -- never commit real credentials to this file.

MMA_API_TOKEN=your-bearer-token-here
